Paper: hep-th/0205043

Date: 2002-05-06

Title: Correspondence Principle in a PP-wave Background

Authors: Miao Li (ITP&NTU)

Comments: v2

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B638 (2002) 155-164

We discuss the correspondence point between a string state and a black hole,in a pp-wave background, and find that the answer is considerably differentfrom that in a flat spacetime background.